data.description: TIME TO COME HOME AND ENJOY YOUR OWN PRIVATE PARADISE..  Upon entrance, you are warmly greeted by slate floors, fresh paint, and seamlessly connecting the kitchen to the living and family room also leading you to your SPARKLING SWIMMINH POOL in your private backyard, perfect for TEXAS SUMMER WEATHER. Kitchen overlooking your private pool with granite countertops, freshly paint cabinets, gas stove and upgraded microwave.  Upstairs an oversized master bedroom with two separate closets, and you'll find a second bathroom, two bedrooms, that provide additional flexibility.   New community walking/jogging trails for new homeowner to enjoy.  Plus community pools, basketball court and many more.. Come and see your next HOME..
